metadata.description: MooTag is set to become the first ever designer brand collection within the Metaverse, with weekly collections dropping in collaboration with artists, influencers & brands. Holders will be rewarded with both virtual and physical items. Moreover, their goal is to open physical boutique stores and reward holders with passive income from those stores! MooTag is a hybrid of the virtual and real world, with fashion being the center of it all.
